Packages 
Package Description
com.xrtb.bidder
Contains the core pieces of the bidding engine.
com.xrtb.commands
The REDIS commands and response objects are in this package.
com.xrtb.common
Miscellaneous tools of the vidding engine are found here.
com.xrtb.db
Contains a very simple database structure, as a hashmap, for use with the administration portal The intent is to be as simple as possible.
com.xrtb.exchanges
The exchange class handlers are in this package.
com.xrtb.geo
Geo location capabilities are implemented here.
com.xrtb.pojo
Common objects used by the engine: bid request, bid, and win object are implemented in this pakage.
com.xrtb.tests
JUNIT test cases are located here.
